```
       IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
       PROGRAM-ID. CUSTUPD.
       ENVIRONMENT DIVISION.
       INPUT-OUTPUT SECTION.
       FILE-CONTROL.
           SELECT CUST-FILE ASSIGN TO CUSTIN
                  ORGANIZATION IS SEQUENTIAL.
       DATA DIVISION.
       FILE SECTION.
       FD  CUST-FILE.
       01  CUST-REC-IN PIC X(80).
       WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
       01  WS-EOF-SWITCH       PIC X(01) VALUE 'N'.
       COPY CUSTREC.
       PROCEDURE DIVISION.
       0000-MAIN-PROCESSING.
           OPEN INPUT CUST-FILE
           PERFORM 1000-PROCESS-RECORDS
               UNTIL WS-EOF-SWITCH = 'Y'
           CLOSE CUST-FILE
           STOP RUN.
       1000-PROCESS-RECORDS.
           READ CUST-FILE INTO CUSTOMER-RECORD
               AT END
                   MOVE 'Y' TO WS-EOF-SWITCH
               NOT AT END
                   PERFORM 2000-UPDATE-CUSTOMER
           END-READ.
       2000-UPDATE-CUSTOMER.
           IF CUST-STATUS = 'A'
               MOVE '555-1234' TO CUST-PHONE
           END-IF
           COMPUTE CUST-BALANCE = CUST-BALANCE * 1.05
       3000-EXIT.
           EXIT.
